<p>Contract farming is based on a pre-harvest agreement between buyer and seller. (<strong>concurrent</strong> list) but agri in state list.</p>
<p>facilitative not regulatory.</p>
<p>NEED&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>poor price discovery + farmer distress + non remunerative MSP + market uncertainity + private participation</li></ol>
<h3>Model Contract farming act, 2018</h3>
<p>1. protects interest of farmers, available for all categories (livestock, dairy, poultry, horticulture, agro forestry)&nbsp; + for all service in agri value chain&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. FPO based promotion of contract farming</p>
<p>3. bars transfer of ownership of land</p>
<p>4. No stock limit for buyers under this act.</p>
